{"tid":496768,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[開箱]入門 Corsair 滑鼠","createTime":"2017-12-12T04:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T11:36:13.000Z","uid":102587,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"163ed73aeb868dbd789aa26a70030881c618c532","tid":496768,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"今次呢隻 靚價 $160左右入手，<br />\n<br />\n入門打機mouse，呢隻應該算冇敵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/123707_2bfd3e0ba516492513d84b96f2643dbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F123707_2bfd3e0ba516492513d84b96f2643dbd.jpg&h=bd734966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHarpoon RGB，外盒有殘體，你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/123727_ab69701f09bb2a875a8a35686497ac1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F123727_ab69701f09bb2a875a8a35686497ac1e.jpg&h=4d8e3f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/123836_2f65632420721083ec0b30eefa519344.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F123836_2f65632420721083ec0b30eefa519344.jpg&h=5f1a52c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開箱，用左常見的 Corsair USB，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/123950_fb9c5148e4da360f08671916315c291f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F123950_fb9c5148e4da360f08671916315c291f.jpg&h=4262574f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滑鼠表面，磨砂感極之強烈，加上入工體學，手感一流。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/124213_d51f475a26848611f2ab602c69f3acbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F124213_d51f475a26848611f2ab602c69f3acbe.jpg&h=dcef9cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後記:<br />\n<br />\n呢隻Harpoon ， 入門有RGB，有Driver，有Marco，有Re-map Key， 重有埋Sinper Mode(要犧牲一個Key)，其實唔差，Sensor 佢只係提及用左光學高精準度，並冇話咩勁牌子。<br />\n按鍵都有 日系Omron，  回饋有力。<br />\n<br />\n相對Steelseries Rival 100， Rival 100 有更強的 準確度，但 手感不如 Harpoon 出色，我諗係咁多喇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"aa1663ba93ddecd777df87745709d609e5574686","tid":496768,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"又細又高，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf26eba35183e9c35afeef34b6a720cf32499715","tid":496768,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又細又高，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好睇手感都好主觀，我有唔少朋友都用大手撚專用既 Rival 700，<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔太適合"},{"pid":"ea14a25e6201d990a44621a9bacb7f1adaf2a16c","tid":496768,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又細又高，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好睇手感都好主觀，我有唔少朋友都用大手撚專用既 Rival 700，<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔太適合</blockquote><br />\n用緊310幾岩我手型，試過logitech 903 603唔係幾岩我"},{"pid":"2f8aae7d3f9fbfaf1bff1e8374de858cd167c928","tid":496768,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又細又高，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好睇手感都好主觀，我有唔少朋友都用大手撚專用既 Rival 700，<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔太適合</blockquote><br />\n用緊310幾岩我手型，試過logitech 903 603唔係幾岩我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n903 太扁平，<br />\n<br />\n同Logi，不了。"},{"pid":"116509c39d5f7cfe04e3e635a94482a521db3061","tid":496768,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"